      h1 Data Table
      p Data tables display sets of raw data. They usually appear in desktop enterprise products
      h2(data-device-preview="../docs-demos/data-table.html") Data Table Layout
      p Common Data Table layout could be treat as the following:
      pre
        code
          :code
            <div class="data-table">
              <table>
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th class="label-cell">Desert (100g serving)</th>
                    <th class="numeric-cell">Calories</th>
                    ...
                    <th class="tablet-only">Comment</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="label-cell">Frozen yogurt</td>
                    <td class="numeric-cell">159</td>
                    ...
                    <td class="tablet-only">I like it!</td>
                  </tr>
                  ...
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
      p Within <a href="./cards.jade">Card</a>:
      pre
        code
          :code
            <div class="data-table card">
              <table>
                ...
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                ...
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
      p Where
      ul
        li <code>data-table</code> - main Data Table wrapper. Required
          ul
            li <code>table</code> - table itself. Required
              ul
                li <code>thead</code> - table head
                li <code>tbody</code> - table body. Required
                li <code>label-cell</code> - main label cell (only one such kind of cell per row, usually first cell)
                li <code>numeric-cell</code> - cell to display numeric data (right-aligned)
                li <code>tablet-only</code> - additional class to show this cell/column only on wide tablet devices (iPad)
      h2(data-device-preview="../docs-demos/data-table-selectable.html") Selectable Rows
      pre
        code
          :code
            <div class="data-table data-table-init card">
              <table>
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th class="checkbox-cell">
                      <label class="form-checkbox">
                        <input type="checkbox"/><i></i>
                      </label>
                    </th>
                    <th class="label-cell">Desert (100g serving)</th>
                    <th class="numeric-cell">Calories</th>
                    ...
                    <th class="numeric-cell">Protein (g)</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="checkbox-cell">
                      <label class="form-checkbox">
                        <input type="checkbox"/><i></i>
                      </label>
                    </td>
                    <td class="label-cell">Frozen yogurt</td>
                    <td class="numeric-cell">159</td>
                    ...
                    <td class="numeric-cell">4.0</td>
                  </tr>
                  ...
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
      p Where
      ul
        li <code>data-table-init</code> - additional class to enable JavaScript action required for selectable rows
        li
          p Checkbox cell. Such cell in table header will select/deselect all rows in table body:
          pre
            code
              :code
                <td class="checkbox-cell">
                  <label class="form-checkbox">
                    <input type="checkbox"/><i></i>
                  </label>
                </td>
      h2(data-device-preview="../docs-demos/data-table-title.html") Table Title/Header
      p When data table is used within <a href="./cards.html">Card</a> it is possible to use additional data table title with actions in card header.
      h4 With title and actions
      pre
        code
          :code
            <div class="data-table data-table-init card">
              <!-- Card Header -->
              <div class="card-header">
                <!-- Table title -->
                <div class="data-table-title">Nutrition</div>
                <!-- Table actions -->
                <div class="data-table-actions">
                  <a class="link icon-only"><i class="icon f7-icons">sort</i></a>
                  <a class="link icon-only"><i class="icon f7-icons">more_vertical_round</i></a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Card Content -->
              <div class="card-content">
                <table>
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                      <th class="checkbox-cell">
                        <label class="form-checkbox">
                          <input type="checkbox"><i></i>
                        </label>
                      </th>
                      <th class="label-cell">Desert (100g serving)</th>
                      <th class="numeric-cell">Calories</th>
                      ...
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="checkbox-cell">
                        <label class="form-checkbox">
                          <input type="checkbox"><i></i>
                        </label>
                      </td>
                      <td class="label-cell">Frozen yogurt</td>
                      <td class="numeric-cell">159</td>
                      ...
                    </tr>
                    ...
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>
      p Where
      ul
        li <code>data-table-title</code> - table title
        li <code>data-table-actions</code> - main table actions
      h4 Different actions on select
      pre
        code
          :code
            <div class="data-table data-table-init card">
              <!-- Card header -->
              <div class="card-header">
                <!-- Default table header -->
                <div class="data-table-header">
                  <!-- Default table title -->
                  <div class="data-table-title">Nutrition</div>
                  <!-- Default table actions -->
