      p Where
      ul
        li <code>data-table-header</code> - default table header. Visible when there are no selected rows
        li <code>data-table-header-selected</code> - selected table header. Visible when there are selected rows
        li <code>data-table-selected-count</code> - count of selected table rows. Number will be placed here by JavaScript
      h3 Alternate header with row actions
